// aivi.random: secure entropy tasks.
//
// `RandomError`, `randomInt`, and `randomBytes` are resolved through the
// compiler's intrinsic catalog (IntrinsicValue::RandomInt /
// IntrinsicValue::RandomBytes). No source-level declarations are needed;
// the import metadata is injected directly at import-resolution time.
//
// There is no long-lived @source for randomness in the first wave.
// Seeded or replayable PRNG surfaces are deferred to a later phase.
